HAI 1.4
    I HAS A nums ITZ A BUKKIT
    nums HAS A 0 ITZ 42
    nums HAS A 1 ITZ 17
    nums HAS A 2 ITZ 99
    nums HAS A 3 ITZ 3
    nums HAS A 4 ITZ 55

    I HAS A minimum ITZ nums'Z SRS 0
    I HAS A maximum ITZ nums'Z SRS 0
    I HAS A i ITZ 1
    IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN 5
        I HAS A val ITZ nums'Z SRS i
        minimum R SMALLR OF minimum AN val
        maximum R BIGGR OF maximum AN val
    IM OUTTA YR loop
    VISIBLE "MIN: " AN minimum
    VISIBLE "MAX: " AN maximum
KTHXBYE
